OL,3,CLiverpool boss Arne Slot given two-
OL,4,Cmatch touchline ban
OL,6,FLiverpool head coach Arne Slot has
OL,7,Fbeen handed a two-match touchline ban
OL,8,Fand a #70,000 fine following his red
OL,9,Fcard during the Merseyside derby.
OL,11,FThe Dutchman, 46, and his assistant
OL,12,FSipke Hulshoff, were both sent off by
OL,13,Freferee Michael Oliver after the final
OL,14,Fwhistle following a 2-2 draw with
OL,15,FEverton at Goodison Park on 12
OL,16,FFebruary.
