OL,3,CLiverpool boss Arne Slot given two-
OL,4,Cmatch touchline ban
OL,6,FAn independent regulatory commission
OL,7,Fhas now hit them both with touchline
OL,8,Fbans after they admitted charges of
OL,9,Fusing an improper manner and/or using
OL,10,Finsulting and/or abusive words and/or
OL,11,Fbehaviour towards both the match
OL,12,Fofficials, with Slot to pay a fine of
OL,13,F#70,000 and Hulshoff #7,000.
OL,15,FAdditionally Everton have been fined
OL,16,F#65,000 and Liverpool #50,000 for
OL,17,Ffailing to ensure their players and/or
OL,18,Fstaff did not behave in an improper
OL,19,Fway.
