OL,3,CLiverpool boss Arne Slot given two-
OL,4,Cmatch touchline ban
OL,6,FSlot and Hulshoff were both dismissed
OL,7,Fafter approaching Oliver after the
OL,8,Ffinal whistle. Speaking about the
OL,9,Fincident at a press conference two
OL,10,Fdays later, Slot admitted his emotions
OL,11,Fhad got the better of him and he had
OL,12,F"made the wrong decision".
OL,14,F"I should have acted differently after
OL,15,Fthe game, but it's an emotional sport
OL,16,Fand sometimes individuals make wrong
OL,17,Fdecisions and that's definitely what I
OL,18,Fdid," the Dutchman said.
