OL,3,CLiverpool boss Arne Slot given two-
OL,4,Cmatch touchline ban
OL,6,FJones and Doucoure clashed after the
OL,7,FEverton player celebrated in front of
OL,8,Fthe Liverpool fans, leading Jones to
OL,9,Fconfront him before players and staff
OL,10,Ffrom both sides raced over.
OL,12,FThe head coach will begin his ban on
OL,13,F26 February when Liverpool take on
OL,14,FNewcastle at Anfield.
OL,16,FHe will return to the touchline for
OL,17,Fthe Champions League match-up with
OL,18,FParis Saint-Germain on Wednesday, 5
OL,19,FMarch, due to it being a UEFA
OL,20,Fcompetition and thus not being
OL,21,Fincluded in the ban.
